<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idab68d174-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5" identifier="/us/usc/t10/s9239"><num value="9239">§ 9239.</num><heading> Enlisted members: officers not to use as servants</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">No officer of the Air Force or the Space Force may use an enlisted member of the Air Force or the Space Force as a servant.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idab68d175-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5">(<ref href="/us/act/1956-08-10/ch1041">Aug. 10, 1956, ch. 1041</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/70A/533">70A Stat. 533</ref>, § 8639; renumbered § 9239, <ref href="/us/pl/115/232/dA/tVIII/s806/b/8">Pub. L. 115–232, div. A, title VIII, § 806(b)(8)</ref>, <date date="2018-08-13">Aug. 13, 2018</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/132/1833">132 Stat. 1833</ref>; amended <ref href="/us/pl/116/283/dA/tIX/s923/c/8">Pub. L. 116–283, div. A, title IX, § 923(c)(8)</ref>, <date date="2021-01-01">Jan. 1, 2021</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/134/3811">134 Stat. 3811</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
